        <tr><td width="68">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="436" class="texte">Combining a strong team spirit with a large dose of company-wide ambition, each team member is devoted to carrying out the somewhat crazy task of making this young Bordeaux-based start-up the world leader in Connected Mobile Games. A further specific feature of the company is its powerful marketing team, already representing a third of the company's headcount, and responsible for the conception of new quality products in accordance with market demands. In-Fusio's internal games development team currently numbers 20 people, and the pressure is on if the company is to reach its target of over 100 employees by the end of this year!<p>&nbsp;</p>
